<p>I have an Issue on Boot Receiver BroadcastReceiver. The Broadcast Receiver is not fired after phone is booted eg. Restart phone or normal start phone.Actually I want to start a Service after firing this.</p>  <p>My Menifest.xml is like this: </p>  <pre><code>&lt;uses-permission android:name="android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED" /&gt;         &lt;application android:name="MY_PACKAGE_NAME.MyCustomApplicationClass"&gt;      &lt;receiver                 android:name="MY_PACKAGE_NAME.BootStartUpReciever"                 android:enabled="true"                 android:exported="true" &gt;                 &lt;intent-filter&gt;                     &lt;action android:name="android.intent.action.BOOT_COMPLETED" /&gt;                     &lt;action android:name="android.intent.action.QUICKBOOT_POWERON" /&gt;                 &lt;/intent-filter&gt;             &lt;/receiver&gt;     &lt;/application&gt; </code></pre>  <p>My BroadcastReceiver is like this:</p>  <pre><code> public class BootStartUpReciever extends BroadcastReceiver{      @Override     public void onReceive(Context context, Intent intent) {         Toast.makeText(context,      "Boot Completed Succesfully",     Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show();     }     } </code></pre>  <p><strong>Notes</strong>: </p>  <ol> <li>My Application has launcher activity.</li> <li>My Application is installed in Internal Memory</li> <li>I Initialize all of things into <code>MyCustomApplicationClass.java</code> class</li> <li>I just want to start a background service after phone boot completing.</li> <li><strong>In this SCENARIO it will just start only a background service not open any Activity.</strong></li> </ol>  <p>I have already read some of thread related to this issue. Unfortunately none of them worked for me. This Threads are:</p>  <ol> <li><a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/7978403/boot-receiver-not-work">Boot Receiver not work</a></li> <li><a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/21444824/boot-complete-and-action-shutdown-never-call-the-broadcastreceiver">BOOT_COMPLETE and ACTION_SHUTDOWN never call the BroadcastReceiver</a></li> <li><a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/16691806/android-why-i-am-not-receiving-the-boot-completed-intent">Android: Why I am not receiving the BOOT_COMPLETED intent?</a></li> <li><a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/10411731/how-to-get-boot-complete-intent-in-htc-when-i-use-poweroff-for-reboot">How to get Boot_Complete intent in HTC when i use &#39;poweroff&#39; for reboot?</a></li> <li><a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/31186001/broadcastreceiver-when-no-launcher-is-present-on-kitkat">BroadcastReceiver when no LAUNCHER is present, on Kitkat</a></li> <li><a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/2784441/trying-to-start-a-service-on-boot-on-android">Trying to start a service on boot on Android</a></li> </ol>  <p>Sorry for bad English.</p>